; Coverage test for commodity.cc
; Tests commodity_t::compare_by_commodity with annotated commodities.
; recursive price comparison when commodity symbols match
; tag comparison between annotated commodities
; final return 0 when all attributes match
; put_commodity XML output path
; Using --lots forces comparison of full commodity annotations including
; lot prices, dates, and tags.

2024/01/15 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage          10 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/01/15] (lot1)
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/20 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage          10 AAPL {$155.00} [2024/01/20] (lot2)
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/25 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage          5 GOOG {$100.00} [2024/01/25] (lotG)
    Assets:Cash

test bal --flat --lots
10 AAPL {$150} [2024/01/15] (lot1)
10 AAPL {$155} [2024/01/20] (lot2)
5 GOOG {$100} [2024/01/25] (lotG)  Assets:Brokerage
-10 AAPL {$150} [2024/01/15] (lot1)
-10 AAPL {$155} [2024/01/20] (lot2)
-5 GOOG {$100} [2024/01/25] (lotG)  Assets:Cash
--------------------
                   0
end test
